Review this code for Phase 7: Add Task Functionality

GOAL:  Implement adding new tasks via input field.

ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA:
- Clicking Add button creates new task with input text
- Pressing Enter in input field creates new task
- Empty or whitespace-only submissions are ignored (no blank tasks created)
- Input field clears after successful task addition
- Input field receives focus after task addition
- New tasks appear at the bottom of the list
- New tasks are saved to localStorage immediately

